assessment_details.task_description:
This assessment requires you to develop your own poster size (A3) Career Attainment Plan covering the elements below. This information is to be presented as a poster for assessment and in addition, it should be submitted as a Word file via Turnitin (A4, Times New Roman, 12 pt., 1½ spacing). You should present your poster in a professional manner that demonstrates its importance to you. You may be asked to present a brief 3-5 minute summary of your Career Attainment Plan within class time.

1. Your 5 year goals over different career stages;

2. The gaps between your current situation and your desired future e.g. personal values, strengths and weaknesses; capability assessment; developmental needs;

3. Career search activities, including the targeted companies you will approach for employment (with any outcomes from search activities);

4. Your Personal Development Plan to will assist you take the next steps to promote as you continue through your career; and

5. Your Personal Brand e.g. LinkedIn profile.

Criteria & Marking:

A marking rubric containing details of the requirement, format, and marking criteria will be discussed in class.
